TITLE: Creating a Tailwind CSS Class Utility Function
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript utility that creates a helper function for conditionally merging Tailwind CSS classes. Uses clsx and tailwind-merge to handle class combinations efficiently and prevent class conflicts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/evil1morty/shadcn-svelte/blob/next-tailwind-4/sites/docs/src/content/installation/manual.md#2025-04-15_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { type ClassValue, clsx } from "clsx";
import { twMerge } from "tailwind-merge";

export function cn(...inputs: ClassValue[]) {
  return twMerge(clsx(inputs));
}
```

